name: Phases in-between; symmetrical dreams.
description:
1/1 special music edition.
Only one in existence; always has been; always will be. The depth of this piece sings to me; does it sing to you? I hope it does, and I wish for you to dance in adjacency to this abstraction to welcome deeper possibilities for your own expressions of abstraction. Let this expand your inner realms; as it did mine.
